PrecisReappointment of DAVID BEVAN of Ottawa, Ontario, as Chairperson of the Board of Directors of the Freshwater Fish Marketing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, or until such time as a new Chairperson is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective August 26, 2016.
